1
00:00:00,414 --> 00:00:04,938
笙ｪA little bit sorry for my love for you笙ｪ

2
00:00:04,938 --> 00:00:10,442
笙ｪSorry, I was a little late笙ｪ

3
00:00:10,442 --> 00:00:16,870
笙ｪI really want the unconscious longing
to appear faster笙ｪ

4
00:00:16,870 --> 00:00:21,350
笙ｪCan I get closer
and hear you say "I do" once more笙ｪ

5
00:00:21,350 --> 00:00:25,798
笙ｪHolding hands, the scenery
in midsummer is a new journey笙ｪ

6
00:00:25,798 --> 00:00:30,709
笙ｪThe chapters of a fairy tale
are performed one after another笙ｪ

7
00:00:30,709 --> 00:00:34,758
笙ｪThe promised moment
will definitely not be forgotten笙ｪ

8
00:00:34,758 --> 00:00:39,293
笙ｪCan I get closer and listen to
the frequency of your heartbeat笙ｪ

9
00:00:39,293 --> 00:00:43,590
笙ｪStart the countdown 4321,
a new scenery笙ｪ

10
00:00:43,590 --> 00:00:48,355
笙ｪI want to see all the scenes about you笙ｪ

11
00:00:48,355 --> 00:00:51,846
笙ｪNo need to miss you anymore笙ｪ

12
00:00:51,846 --> 00:00:55,526
笙ｪRight by your side笙ｪ

13
00:00:57,172 --> 00:01:00,550
=Jin Secretary=

14
00:01:00,550 --> 00:01:03,238
=Episode 24=

15
00:01:03,473 --> 00:01:07,891
(Half an hour ago)

16
00:01:11,533 --> 00:01:13,866
Can I put my hands down now?

17
00:01:14,720 --> 00:01:15,866
Yes.

18
00:01:26,966 --> 00:01:31,000
I'm fine. This job is indeed too tiring.

19
00:01:31,300 --> 00:01:33,100
Xi'en, you go to work tomorrow.

20
00:01:33,100 --> 00:01:34,733
- Xi'en is still...
- Mom, I'm fine.

21
00:01:36,633 --> 00:01:40,633
Yes, I've done so much for you,

22
00:01:42,566 --> 00:01:45,933
but you've only blamed
but never thanked me.

23
00:01:47,366 --> 00:01:49,133
Then why do I make myself so tired?

24
00:01:51,233 --> 00:01:55,366
Xi'en, happy birthday.

25
00:01:59,966 --> 00:02:00,966
May you be happy.

26
00:02:08,933 --> 00:02:11,833
What's going on, boss?

27
00:02:15,900 --> 00:02:17,000
Every day I spend with you

28
00:02:20,000 --> 00:02:21,600
is the most wonderful for me.

29
00:02:23,933 --> 00:02:25,200
You're like the sunshine,

30
00:02:26,533 --> 00:02:27,933
shining into my life.

31
00:02:30,633 --> 00:02:32,366
Although I am really too perfect,

32
00:02:34,000 --> 00:02:35,733
you were not scared away
by my brilliance.

33
00:02:38,566 --> 00:02:39,766
Although you always hit me,

34
00:02:40,966 --> 00:02:42,433
I have suddenly gotten used to it.

35
00:02:47,233 --> 00:02:51,033
After meeting you, I learned to trust,

36
00:02:52,533 --> 00:02:53,433
to be myself,

37
00:02:55,366 --> 00:02:56,333
and to love.

38
00:02:58,900 --> 00:03:00,800
I remember the starry sky
we watched together.

39
00:03:02,700 --> 00:03:03,712
It was so beautiful.

40
00:03:05,166 --> 00:03:06,233
I suddenly realized

41
00:03:07,366 --> 00:03:09,400
the person I want to stargaze with

42
00:03:11,366 --> 00:03:12,433
is you,

43
00:03:13,533 --> 00:03:14,400
Jin Xi'en.

44
00:03:46,200 --> 00:03:47,456
Look at the screen.

45
00:03:50,833 --> 00:03:52,833
(The above is the objective
and true situation.)

46
00:03:55,233 --> 00:03:56,933
(At today's press conferences,)

47
00:03:57,166 --> 00:03:59,133
(I have good news
to share with everyone.)

48
00:03:59,433 --> 00:04:02,233
(My girlfriend is my secretary,)

49
00:04:02,933 --> 00:04:03,800
(Jin Xi'en.)

50
00:04:05,108 --> 00:04:08,892
笙ｪWho abandoned our past笙ｪ

51
00:04:08,892 --> 00:04:12,733
笙ｪLet the fireworks vanish completely笙ｪ

52
00:04:12,733 --> 00:04:14,133
Will you be my girlfriend?

53
00:04:14,133 --> 00:04:15,813
笙ｪA moment of awakening笙ｪ

54
00:04:15,813 --> 00:04:18,574
笙ｪWe repeatedly start a journey笙ｪ

55
00:04:18,574 --> 00:04:21,089
笙ｪLove is like a shooting star笙ｪ

56
00:04:21,089 --> 00:04:24,352
笙ｪTaking away the wishes
that never come true笙ｪ

57
00:04:24,352 --> 00:04:25,833
笙ｪThe trace of time笙ｪ

58
00:04:25,833 --> 00:04:28,166
This used to be the scene I dreamed of.

59
00:04:29,633 --> 00:04:32,600
But, boss,

60
00:04:35,533 --> 00:04:39,100
we may not
have known each other long enough.

61
00:04:40,133 --> 00:04:43,033
You may discover the person you love

62
00:04:44,400 --> 00:04:45,600
may not be me.

63
00:04:53,600 --> 00:04:55,200
I'm certain I love you.

64
00:04:57,400 --> 00:04:59,366
Let's spend more time together.

65
00:04:59,366 --> 00:05:02,460
笙ｪThe reality has shocked me笙ｪ

66
00:05:02,460 --> 00:05:07,648
笙ｪI'm ignored by you笙ｪ

67
00:05:07,648 --> 00:05:11,133
笙ｪHow to track your traces笙ｪ

68
00:05:11,133 --> 00:05:15,872
笙ｪI know you never really cared笙ｪ

69
00:05:19,000 --> 00:05:21,633
How is the financing plan
of WE Beauty Group?

70
00:05:22,833 --> 00:05:24,566
It's a bad plan.

71
00:05:24,833 --> 00:05:27,366
Impossible. Mr. Lan
and I both think the plan is good.

72
00:05:30,633 --> 00:05:34,300
If you think so,
I'll have nothing to say.

73
00:05:41,433 --> 00:05:42,366
Miss Jin!

74
00:05:44,694 --> 00:05:46,449
笙ｪOpen my secret笙ｪ

75
00:05:46,449 --> 00:05:50,033
笙ｪI hope you find
all the tenderness hidden for you笙ｪ

76
00:05:50,033 --> 00:05:51,100
Why?

77
00:05:52,118 --> 00:05:54,016
笙ｪSinking into your love笙ｪ

78
00:05:54,016 --> 00:05:59,566
笙ｪWith each breath,
I can feel the sweetness笙ｪ

79
00:05:59,566 --> 00:06:00,896
Are you eating?

80
00:06:02,033 --> 00:06:05,633
Mr. Lan, it seems
the rain is pretty heavy.

81
00:06:08,133 --> 00:06:09,300
I haven't eaten yet.

82
00:06:09,433 --> 00:06:11,100
Can I join you?

83
00:06:11,600 --> 00:06:14,133
Sure. Waitress, one more person.

84
00:06:18,000 --> 00:06:20,200
Miss Jin, sit down.

85
00:06:23,633 --> 00:06:25,800
Mr. Lan, I'm off...

86
00:06:25,800 --> 00:06:27,040
Miss Jin.

87
00:06:36,700 --> 00:06:38,433
Mr. Lan.

88
00:06:38,433 --> 00:06:41,866
I watched your press conference today.
Very impressive.

89
00:06:42,566 --> 00:06:44,533
Here, I toast to you.

90
00:06:46,700 --> 00:06:49,933
Mr. Zeng is steady and mature,

91
00:06:51,033 --> 00:06:53,400
making people feel secure.

92
00:06:54,033 --> 00:06:57,366
Whether a business partner or a lover,

93
00:06:57,566 --> 00:06:59,233
you're one of the best choices.

94
00:06:59,400 --> 00:07:00,333
Isn't that right, Miss Jin?

95
00:07:05,166 --> 00:07:06,433
Mr. Lan, I'm flattered.

96
00:07:08,833 --> 00:07:12,233
I'm being honest.
You're pragmatic and wealthy.

97
00:07:12,733 --> 00:07:13,733
Unfortunately,

98
00:07:14,200 --> 00:07:15,800
my family is currently
in financial trouble.

99
00:07:16,033 --> 00:07:17,433
I have to be cautious every day.

100
00:07:18,233 --> 00:07:22,166
If it were up to me,
I'd also choose the best.

101
00:07:28,533 --> 00:07:29,800
What's wrong with you, Lan Chen?

102
00:07:32,166 --> 00:07:35,166
Me? Miss Jin,

103
00:07:36,333 --> 00:07:38,500
Lihuai International
is an important client.

104
00:07:38,500 --> 00:07:42,500
Many people long for having a meal
with Mr. Zeng.

105
00:07:44,800 --> 00:07:46,433
Miss Jin.

106
00:07:46,433 --> 00:07:48,900
You shouldn't be greedy
of such good wine.

107
00:08:02,133 --> 00:08:03,392
Come on.

108
00:08:05,566 --> 00:08:09,933
People always struggle upwards. So to...

109
00:08:09,933 --> 00:08:12,733
To your company's new products.

110
00:08:13,766 --> 00:08:14,944
Come on.

111
00:08:31,966 --> 00:08:35,000
It's fine to struggle upwards,

112
00:08:35,400 --> 00:08:37,133
but they should take one step at a time.

113
00:08:37,133 --> 00:08:38,733
Don't take too big steps,

114
00:08:39,300 --> 00:08:40,500
or it's easy to hurt themselves.

115
00:08:41,833 --> 00:08:44,133
Don't think of an overnight success.

116
00:08:44,766 --> 00:08:46,733
Sometimes, the higher you fly,

117
00:08:48,400 --> 00:08:49,766
the harder you fall.

118
00:08:52,166 --> 00:08:55,433
Mr. Lan, is there some misunderstanding?

119
00:09:07,633 --> 00:09:09,433
Waitress, another bottle of wine.

120
00:09:09,766 --> 00:09:11,166
What's wrong with you, Lan Chen?

121
00:09:11,166 --> 00:09:14,570
笙ｪI want to escape笙ｪ

122
00:09:14,570 --> 00:09:16,640
笙ｪLove is like a trap笙ｪ

123
00:09:16,640 --> 00:09:19,968
笙ｪA well-designed illusion笙ｪ

124
00:09:19,968 --> 00:09:21,897
笙ｪYou're the one笙ｪ

125
00:09:21,897 --> 00:09:25,833
笙ｪWho abandoned our past笙ｪ

126
00:09:25,833 --> 00:09:28,500
No, there's no misunderstanding.

127
00:09:30,700 --> 00:09:33,433
We're just business partners.

128
00:09:34,366 --> 00:09:38,333
I need your investment
and try to make more money for you.

129
00:09:42,333 --> 00:09:45,633
I pay you a salary, and you work for me.

130
00:09:49,700 --> 00:09:50,800
Don't be late for work tomorrow.

131
00:09:55,100 --> 00:09:58,133
By the way, Miss Jin,
you did a good job today.

132
00:09:58,700 --> 00:10:00,600
You've learned a lot from me.

133
00:10:01,933 --> 00:10:03,966
You should thank me.

134
00:10:04,333 --> 00:10:06,166
Good for you, anyway.

135
00:10:09,233 --> 00:10:10,272
Mr. Zeng,

136
00:10:12,672 --> 00:10:17,952
thank you for the dinner.
Looking forward to working together.

137
00:10:23,733 --> 00:10:24,699
Lan Chen.

138
00:10:25,200 --> 00:10:26,400
Lan Chen.

139
00:10:30,948 --> 00:10:35,470
笙ｪI pass through the crowd with you笙ｪ

140
00:10:38,500 --> 00:10:43,461
笙ｪAs if we have a tacit understanding,
attracting each other笙ｪ

141
00:10:46,510 --> 00:10:52,334
笙ｪWhen the loneliness cracks,
warmth seeps in笙ｪ

142
00:10:52,334 --> 00:10:59,804
笙ｪYou come with light,
shining into my heart笙ｪ

143
00:10:59,804 --> 00:11:03,285
笙ｪStars fall into my eyes,
and you fall into my heart笙ｪ

144
00:11:03,285 --> 00:11:07,406
笙ｪI make a wish foolishly,
but actually, you are the shooting star笙ｪ

145
00:11:07,406 --> 00:11:09,102
笙ｪOpen my secret笙ｪ

146
00:11:09,102 --> 00:11:15,150
笙ｪI hope you find
all the tenderness hidden for you笙ｪ

147
00:11:15,150 --> 00:11:19,022
笙ｪSinking into your love,
I want to sink deeper笙ｪ

148
00:11:19,022 --> 00:11:23,528
笙ｪWith each breath,
I can feel the sweetness笙ｪ

149
00:11:23,528 --> 00:11:32,238
笙ｪTwo lonely islands meet,
and it's the gift of fate笙ｪ
